    "Moreover, most schemes did not provide the numerical value of latency, therefore we examined the suggested scheme based on the work process of the design schemes, attack prevention mechanism, and the data verification process.",
    "While evaluating a clear difference was evident that the majority of the scheme suffers from high latency.",
    "Compagno et al. (2013) suffer from high latency due to the verification of each chunk hash with the provider signature in every intermediate router between the consumer and the content provider.",
    "Similarly, Kim et al. (2015) suffer from high latency due to the verification of each interest and content that passes from the CCNCheck.",
    "Additionally, Ghall et al. (2014a); Ghali et al. (2014b Ghali et al. (, 2014c)) are affected by high latency as every interest will wait until the Key Locator field attaches the provider public key with interest in the NDN routers."
  ],
